Description: Will an invitation to a ball lead to Negi learning more truths or is it a trap?
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 29
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy. How will she survive the pursuit of demons who want the power in her blood?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 8
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy. In this volume: has the temporary safe haven dulled their edge? No worries, there are secrets even here.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 4
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human? In this volume: a curry battle to the finish!
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 5
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 1
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: Amu has three guardians who are helping her discover her true self. In this volume: graduation nears and a new guardian emerges from Ikuto’s violin.
Title: SHUGO CHARA!, VOL. 10
Author: Peach-Pit

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards. In this volume, a civil war brews.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 13
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: In a dark future Zoichi Kanoe fights to save humanity from the N5S virus that has turned the earth earth population into zombie-like drones. This volume concludes the series.
Title: BIOMEGA, VOL. 6
Author: Tsutomu Nihei

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO + VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 4
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry. Do they have what it takes?
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 4
Author: Tsugumi Ohba and Takeshi Obata
Contributor: by Tsugumi Ohba and Takeshi Obata
